race.comment: SUPREME LEADER (3) turned in a plain run last time when eighth at this track over 461m behind Appenzell (26.89) in a OPEN. Was in the money prior to that. Has ability and is a key runner. CADIA GOLD (8) missed the frame latest (26.37) when sixth over 461m at this track in a OPEN. Has already won five times from this draw. Among the main chances. DIP THE DONUT (1) is suited by the inside draw. Latest effort finished 4th over 461m at this track beaten 9 lengths (26.71) behind Young Star in a Grade 4 on November 11. Looks one of the chances. Something for the Multiples: CAL'S SENSATION (7)
